        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-white mb-4">When Should You Choose Auth0?</h2>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
          <div class="p-4 bg-green-500/10 border border-green-500/30 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Auth0 Recommended</h3>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>RBAC/permission management needed</li>
              <li>Enterprise SSO (SAML) required</li>
              <li>Detailed login analytics needed</li>
              <li>MFA is mandatory</li>
              <li>Compliance requirements (SOC2, HIPAA, etc.)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
          <div class="p-4 bg-red-500/10 border border-red-500/30 rounded-xl">
            <h3 class="text-white font-bold mb-2">Consider Alternatives</h3>
            <ul class="text-text-secondary text-sm space-y-1">
              <li>Simple login only → <a href="/en/map/auth/clerk" class="text-primary hover:underline">Clerk</a></li>
              <li>Next.js only → <a href="/en/map/auth/nextauth" class="text-primary hover:underline">NextAuth</a></li>
              <li>Google ecosystem → <a href="/en/map/auth/firebase" class="text-primary hover:underline">Firebase</a></li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <!-- Next Steps -->
      <section class="mb-10">
        <Callout client:load variant="info" title="Next Steps" locale="en">
          <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-1 mt-2">
            <li>
              <a href="https://auth0.com/docs/secure/multi-factor-authentication" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">
                MFA Setup
              </a> - Enable two-factor authentication
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://auth0.com/docs/authenticate/protocols/saml" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">
                SAML SSO
              </a> - Enterprise SSO integration
            </li>
            <li>
              <a href="https://auth0.com/docs/customize/actions" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-primary hover:underline">
                Actions
              </a> - Customize login flows
            </li>
          </ul>
        </Callout>
      </section>
    </article>

    <PageNavigation currentPath="/map/auth/auth0" lang="en" />
  </div>
</DocsLayout>
